S3 method for printing RCT_analysis results

# S3 method for bmbstats_RCT_analysis
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

Object of class bmbstats_RCT_analysis
...

Extra arguments. Not used

Examples

set.seed(1666)

data("vertical_jump_data")

rct_model <- RCT_analysis(
  vertical_jump_data,
  group = "Group",
  treatment_label = "Treatment",
  control_label = "Control",
  pre_test = "Pre-test",
  post_test = "Post-test",
  control = model_control(boot_type = "perc", boot_samples = 500)
)
#> Bootstraping: 500 resamples
#> Calculating confidence intervals...
